# Dependencies (recursive)
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions

# Next.js / React builds
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/dist/

# Coverage / testing
**/coverage/
**/.pytest_cache/

# Environment / credentials
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/credentials.json
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/.credentials

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# Misc
**/.DS_Store
**/.vercel/